Clea: Please provide me with the details of the request.

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Ahaha, you've come at a good time! I
have some excellent wine. How about enjoying it together?
Sister Sophia: Oh my, is that alright~!?

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Of course! You're dressed so
provocatively, it's getting me excited!
Maid Amina: Master, it's about time to take them down.

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Ahaha, you always report to me
afterwards! Now, let's talk about the details of the
request.

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: I want you to lend me your power to
help my friend in Canonas.
Clea: Is it your friend in Canonas?

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: You are the younger brother of Queen
Leucos, who passed away, and a member of the Senate, Pilia,
correct?

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: He's got a little problem, so sorry,
but I want you to meet with Amina!

Clea: Understood. I will confirm the details with Lady
Pilia.

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Sigh, I also want to go with you
guys... but I have a job to deliver tribute to Queen Caron.

Maid Amina: Please come back from your playtime in
moderation, okay?

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Of course! There's no way I would
stop by Mucos on the way back!

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Please, I'm begging you to help my
friend with their troubles!

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Canonas Region/Senator Pilia's
Mansion\c[0]

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: 'I heard it from Amina! With
this, Phoni will be able to sleep peacefully too.'

Profligate Noble Lewd: That's right, that's right! Speaking
of the reward...
Clea: We have received a reward from Lady Pilia.

Profligate Noble Lewd: 'Amina, tell me! What is the way to
repay a benefactor?'

Maid Amina: Showing it through actions rather than words,
is that the way an imperial noble should be?

Profligate Noble Lewd: Then it's settled! Let's cooperate
in investigating the dragon.

Profligate Noble Lewd: Just like how adventurers have their
own information network in the Adventurer's Guild, there is
information that only nobles like me can know.

Profligate Noble Lewd: If there is any information related
to the dragon, I will contact you first!

Profligate Noble Lewd: I love seeing girls' smiles! After
we're done with the dragon, I definitely want you to come
here.

Maid Amina: Please refrain from hiring just anyone. Please
put yourself in the shoes of those who take it seriously and
turn them away.

Profligate Noble Lewd: I might end up hiring someone like
this while saying such things, aren't I cute?
Maid Amina: Please stop fooling around... Honestly...

Profligate Noble Lewd: I'll leave the investigation of the
dragon's whereabouts to you.
Maid Amina: Is it really okay?

Profligate Noble Lewd: You can use your time and people
freely. The imperial sky is too narrow for dragons to fly,
you know.

Playboy nobleman Luid: 'Hahaha, isn't this a nice place? If
you like it, you can even live here!'

Playboy nobleman Luid: 'Hey there, glad you came! Did you
come here to play today?'

Clea: Thanks to Luid-san, we found out the whereabouts of
the dragon.
Clea: I came here today to express my gratitude.

Playboy nobleman Luid: That's a very interesting story. Can
you tell me more about it?

Clea: According to the information we gathered, it seems
highly likely that there is a dragon in Mount Monimos.

Clea: Once the investigation and preparations are complete,
I intend to go to the site.

Playboy nobleman Luid: Amina, tell me! When was the last
time I was this surprised?

Maid Amina: It was since the time I was charged for 100
bottles of expensive wine that I didn't even order at the
brothel in Oros.

Playboy nobleman Luid: Can I also help with the dragon
subjugation?
Clea: That's very kind of you, but...

Playboy nobleman Luid: I'm drawn to your earnestness... Not
only that, your heroic actions are a credit to the imperial
nobility!

Playboy nobleman Luid: You can rest assured! Despite my
appearance, I am wealthy, you know!

Maid Amina: I hope you won't regret taking me up on my
offer...

Clea: Thank you very much! If there's anything we need,
I'll be sure to consult with you.
Playboy nobleman Luid: Yeah, you can come anytime!
Clea: What should we do next?

Priestess Sophia: How about meeting with Eleo-chan? The
priests might be willing to cooperate.
Clea: Understood, let's go and see.

The debauched noble, Luid: 'Dragon extermination, huh... I
can't help but feel excited despite my age.'

Playboy nobleman Lloyd: 'Well, let me hear your story! I
shouldn't have done anything to make enemies of the
Adventurer's Guild.'
Clea: Actually, I have a favor to ask.

Playboy nobleman Lloyd: Huh? It's because it was a request
from a cute girl, so I couldn't help myself...

Maid Amina: Sigh... I apologize, but my master has a bit of
a mental illness. It's quite unfortunate.

Clea: Um, I would like to temporarily use Lord Lloyd's
property as a transportation route.
Playboy nobleman Lloyd: Hahaha, I see, I see...!

Playboy nobleman Lloyd: Amina, tell me! Have there been any
issues happening around this mansion recently?

Maid Amina: Yes, my master, many thieves have suddenly
started appearing.

Clea (Could it be... the information about the crystal
transportation has leaked?)

Playboy nobleman Lloyd: I have a condition for lending you
the land. Can I ask you to take care of the thieves?

Playboy nobleman Lloyd: When you're ready, please talk to
Amina.

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: 'Well done! It's the perfect
combination of being serious, beautiful, and strong!'

Maid Amina: You're the complete opposite of a reckless and
weak master, aren't you?

Profligate Noble Lewd: Ahaha, you look like you're about to
cry! Well then, it's my turn to keep my promise, right?

Profligate Noble Lewd: You can freely use my land as
promised, and if you need anything else, don't hesitate to
rely on me!

Profligate Noble Lewd: You can think of it as making a
friend in the Valt region, if you'd like.

Maid Amina: You're getting carried away... Can you just
handle it casually?

Clea: I think Mr. Lewd is someone I can have a favorable
impression of.
Maid Amina: Is that as a member of the Adventurer's Guild?

Clea: No, as an individual, I called you Amina, not as a
maid.
Clea: I thought he was a good person.

Maid Amina: You don't act like an adventurer at all. But be
careful, the words of nobles are lighter than feathers.
Maid Amina: And... well, I've talked too much, haven't I?

Maid Amina: Are you ready? You won't be able to leave the
mansion until this request is completed.

Maid Amina: I would like you to eliminate the thieves who
entered the private property, so please take care of it.

Maid Amina: Please crush them all without leaving a single
one.

Maid Amina: That's a relief. Thanks to that, I'll be able
to sleep peacefully tonight.
